Name:           perl-Number-Range
Version:        0.12
Release:        1%{?dist}
Summary:        Perl extension defining ranges of numbers and testing if a number is found in the range. You can also add and delete from this range
License:        CHECK(Distributable)
Group:          Development/Libraries
